      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in paintwork that retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is original, featuring factory-perfect gaps and a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the color pop in any light. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory floor mats have been protected by weather-proof overlays since day one. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, binder-organized service history documenting every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by senior master technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any oxidation or road grime, reflecting its life as a fair-weather weekend driver. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full synthetic fluid flush and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires. Included with the sale are both original transponder keys, the factory window sticker, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast",
